1. Define the coordinate ring of the flag manifold by generators and relations over \(\mathbb{Z}\).
2. Using the same description by generators and relations, associate a "flag algebra" \(\varLambda^{+}\!E\) to any module \(E\) over any commutative ring \(R\).

